com.interpss.core.aclf.adj

Interface FunctionLoad

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, IAclfAdjustment, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FunctionLoadImpl

    public interface FunctionLoad
extends NameTag, IAclfAdjustment
    A representation of the model object 'Function Load'. Aclf functional load class. - It has two FuncLoad object: P func load and Q func load - P = P0 x ( ap + bpV + cpV^2) - Q = Q0 x ( aq + bqV + cqV^2) - ap + bp + cp = 1.0 and aq + bq + cq = 1.0 Please note the referenced AclfBus has to be a const P load bus. Object id is the same as the busId it reference to.

    The following features are supported:

    • P
    • Q
    • Parent Bus
    See Also:
    AclfAdjustPackage.getFunctionLoad()
